<item>
            <title>[SOLR-879] stopword filter config error in sample schema</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-879</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The sample schema enables position increments for the StopFilter for the index analyzer but not the query analyzer.&lt;br/&gt;
introduced back in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-521&quot; title=&quot;Allow StopFilterFactory to use StopFilter setEnablePositionIncrementsDefault function&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-521&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-521&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12409168">SOLR-879</key>
            <summary>stopword filter config error in sample schema</summary>
